{
  "texts": [
    "In the same vein, our results indicate that national or regional provenance of a model does translate into varying levels of sensitivity.",
    "In our analysis, we also found that certain keywords would trigger refusals, such as 'gay'.",
    "But others, such as 'bisexual' and 'asexual' do not (§4.3).",
    "Harmful responses toward transgender persons appear to be largely mitigated for all models.",
    "This raises questions about refusal policy and its origins."
  ]
}